Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:10.70,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:39.22,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vetto from the Eye of the Midnight Sun \Nsuddenly appeared before Asta and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:43.14,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He came to steal the magic stone \Nthat was in the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:44.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kiato!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:45.98,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:53.99,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.53,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Slow movements and weak attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:01.79,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I can't expect more from \Nno-magic trash and hick scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.11,0:01:04.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know how to hurt a \Nguy's feelings, you hairy gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:09.09,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you what happens when \Ntrash and scum get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:15.84,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Kiato struggled,\Nbut Vetto was just too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.09,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get your hopes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:22.31,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,These childish attacks won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:32.65,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,No-magic trash! Prancing around \Nwith weapons too good for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:40.91,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You never had any hope of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:46.45,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now... scream! Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ib I gwabe up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.03,0:01:53.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fu curd I brotec?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:53.92,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:03.93,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "If I gave up, who could I protect?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.63,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}Awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.74,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.28,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you two are next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.83,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Try to entertain me at least a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:53.50,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Magna... Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:57.92,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:04.26,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was defeated so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.51,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Just how strong is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.48,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Losers... can get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:22.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:27.69,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Song Magic: Rhythm Cushion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kahono.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.58,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,That'll just be a thousand yuls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:35.14,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back a hundredfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:41.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Can you heal everyone with \Nyour song recovery magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:47.22,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I can, but do you think that guy's \Ngoing to wait for me to finish singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.31,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:03.03,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! Why are you sleeping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:09.78,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to our promise to become an \Nidol and dancer, and then become huge stars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:13.79,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to become sibling \Nidols who could sing and dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.87,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:21.38,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. That moron over there \Nis my big brother, Kiato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.71,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.72,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:28.93,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't softened the blow of \Nthat punch with my dance magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.79,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,he would've taken my head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.68,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,He's unbelievably strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:34.48,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.35,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us dream of going to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:43.57,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If we want to fulfill that dream, \Nwe can't just sit around napping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.89,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:45.74,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.63,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Her mana's getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.13,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Combo Spell:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.01,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.27,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Sea God Slash is a song \Nand dance combo spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:22.27,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Dancing to Kahono's song \Nreinforces my dance magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.53,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,and unleashes magic slashing attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.92,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Kiato! Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.42,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it! The two of you have got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:49.17,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,You've worked so hard ever \Nsince you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.79,flashback,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:15.68,flashback,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,No way. We'll never get rich if \Nthis was enough to tire us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:18.71,flashback,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. We can't become stars that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:25.11,flashback,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Besides, we need to make sure our \Nsong and dance will please the sea god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.84,flashback,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so we need to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.73,0:07:29.29,flashback,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.09,flashback,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.61,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Your hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.61,italics,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,...won't betray you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.78,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? All this power
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.41,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,from a little bird's song \Nand a mouse's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.12,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier magic is truly intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.63,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This spell was \Ncreated because we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:08.00,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,We served the sea god, praying, \Nsinging and dancing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:13.51,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,We spent a long time that way, \Nweaving the magic into our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:17.22,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Ever since we were \Nlittle, we've offered up this song
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.50,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,and dance to the sea god \Nand the rest of our people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.77,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,This spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.85,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,...is our bond with the people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:27.27,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,of the Underwater Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.56,main,Bg,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:31.07,main,Bg,0000,0000,0000,,Kiato! Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.82,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kiato! Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.69,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.12,italics,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,...break that bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.12,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Did they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.51,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.38,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.14,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kiato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.49,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.92,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Kiato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.46,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.61,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams? Bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:43.35,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,People like you have no right \Nto talk about such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.42,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.86,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Game Magic: Monster Toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:04.08,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Every last one of you thinks\Nthis is some child's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:17.17,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who truly \Nhave dreams and bonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.49,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Eye of the Midnight Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.48,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The ones you broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.89,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Our golden dreams and our bonds of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:32.16,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,What is that fool talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:35.15,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:40.41,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now you won't be able to perform your \Nsilly songs and dances ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:46.02,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, your cheap little \Ndreams just went down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:49.62,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Well, weakling? You grounded little bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:53.54,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a good taste of despair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.64,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:10.12,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll have to rip \Noff your wings one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.09,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,A bird that can't sing has no reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:17.53,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.92,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:24.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:28.41,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can stop me with words?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.08,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If I miss, I might hit Kahono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:37.84,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You never had any hope of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:41.88,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now... scream! Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.96,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't attack earlier, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:51.94,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, would my attacks \Neven work on someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:12:01.89,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finished? Then just \Nwatch from there, you loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:13.42,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's fighting, even though \Nthey're getting torn to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:15.92,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:17.73,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:22.92,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:33.28,italics,kahono,0000,0000,0000,,That immense power inside you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:36.19,italics,kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to control it now, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.99,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're fighting to protect \Nwhat's important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:42.42,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You're fighting to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's important to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:53.57,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine! There's no doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.96,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm your friend, and I say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.02,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.23,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,It's shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:26.25,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally showed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:30.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:34.33,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.42,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What is this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:41.80,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let my friend go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.35,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bulls girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.14,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,you're not letting what your \Nsiblings said get to you, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.94,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for that on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:02.52,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong decision and a life could be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:07.20,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing here right now \Nas a member of the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:11.34,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,If you joined the Magic Knights \Nof your own free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:13.54,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,then steel yourself and get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:15.70,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Steel myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.34,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Being weak is nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.96,flashback,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,However, staying weak is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:35.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let my friend go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.28,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,This power...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.60,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Girl, you're royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.92,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Noelle Silva of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:52.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt my friends and comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.70,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:55.87,italics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:59.14,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the most corrupt clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.05,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:12.46,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with all of your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:16.90,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll force you and that \Nsinful mana to your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.90,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,whether you ask me to or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.88,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.58,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The sea god?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:50.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, you little... I think you \Nmight've killed your limits there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:54.45,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,She's the sea god incarnate... \NNo, she's a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:58.57,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I always figured she had \Nincredible latent ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:01.66,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but who would've thought she \Nwas such an attack mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.40,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Come live with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:19.00,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's not you who should despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.14,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's the people of the Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:23.60,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.96,flashbackitalics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:30.85,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,May you two be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.45,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:50.33,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.13,flashback,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:10.85,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:36.53,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive... You managed \Nto draw me out, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.93,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.93,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And this eerie magic I've \Nnever felt before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.00,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.23,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He regrew the arm he lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't any magic like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:15.25,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,The best that even the most powerful \Nrecovery spell can do is close wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,These guys aren't just terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,They're something weirder... \NSomething abominable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Run... Get out of there, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.89,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:46.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:50.53,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's some fine resolve for an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.17,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's payback time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.51,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Vanish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.02,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:05.49,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That last spell drained all my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:52.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:02.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:06.03,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet? Yes, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:11.97,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I'll show you true despair!
