Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:49.48,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.85,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Mythical Beast Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:53.85,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Mythical Beast Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:58.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what were you saying during \Nyour mythical beast magic spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:00.67,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, insect. I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:02.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling an insect?! I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.53,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,This is the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.35,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, right? Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:08.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.77,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:11.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:13.32,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:16.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.13,0:23:17.40,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:19.96,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.44,0:23:23.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The only difference between a \Nwhale and a dolphin is their size?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:26.59,sign_33635_243_Udon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Udon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:26.71,sign_33635_244_Somen,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Somen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:26.84,sign_33635_245_Hiyamugi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyamugi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:26.89,main,vetto,0000,0000,0000,,The only difference between udon, somen, \Nand hiyamugi is how thick they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:30.55,sign_33726_246_Hawk,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:30.55,sign_33726_247_Eagle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Eagle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:29.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently hawks and eagles \Nare the same birds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:30.55,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I did not know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:35.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I knew that! I'm a royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:37.77,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,What were we talking about again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:43.81,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Insects, I'm getting tired \Nof your incessant buzzing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:46.69,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you with my own hands, one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.20,0:23:50.86,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 47: "The Only Weapon."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 47\N\N{\fs18} The Only Weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:53.74,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is Mythical Beast Magic!
